data.description: Welcome to the paradise of South Florida, resort-style social living at its absolute best. Enjoy this wonderful ground floor condo with one bedroom, one and one-half bath located in sunny West Palm Beach Florida and experience the distinct Century Village ''way of life'' with luxurious recreational facilities and abundant social activities. Very private outside corner or end unit. Fully furnished on the ground floor of a very well-run and friendly Association. Tile floors throughout. The building is in excellent shape, recently painted and with non-slip walkways.  New roof in 2020. Amenities including a 1200-seat theater, live entertainment, free current run movies, 15 swimming pools, tennis and pickleball, bocce ball, cards, clubs, and fitness center. This ground floor unit is conveniently located between I-95 and the Florida Turnpike, about 8 miles west of the Atlantic Ocean and the gorgeous Palm Beaches and minutes to Palm Beach International Airport. This condo is available for you to enjoy as a year-round home or just an escape from the winter weather.
